  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if taking nitazoxanide alone for 4 weeks followed
      by 36 weeks of nitazoxanide plus peginterferon is superior to peginterferon plus ribavirin
      (standard of care) for 48 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
